Interface IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOp

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IWorkspaceConnection.IDeleteOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IDeleteSubtreeOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IMarkAsMergedOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IMergeOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IMergeResultOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IRelocateOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IRevertOp, IWorkspaceConnection.ISaveOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IUndoMergeOp, IWorkspaceConnection.IUndoOp
    Enclosing interface:
    IWorkspaceConnection

    public static interface IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOp
    Marker interface representing an operation that modifies a workspace configuration. Instances are manufactured by IWorkspaceConnection.IConfigurationOpFactory, and used in IWorkspaceConnection#commit(IChangeSetHandle, Collection).

    0.6 (RTC 1.0)
